Hi Harry,

I did not use POR-15, it was Master-Series (masterseriesct.com). I started
with their silver primer-two coats, then one coat of their high gloss top
coat. I made sure the temps were above the rating on the can...pretty close
to it but above. So hopefully the paint will adhere...it sure is sticking to
my wrist pretty good. As for the brushes-they were dissolving in chunks,
just losing their rigidity...sometimes shrinking a little bit.

-Kevin 

